### ============================================================================
### ADMIN → SYSTEM — /api/v1/admin/system
### ============================================================================

### Get system status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/system/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get system logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/system/logs?level=INFO&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get system settings
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/system/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Update system settings
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/system/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "maintenanceMode": false,
  "maxPlansPerUser": 50
}

### Toggle maintenance mode
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/system/settings/toggle-maintenance
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Fetch live exchange rates
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/system/settings/fetch-live-rates
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
